  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, I didn't listen to the wireless, I just felt happy that morning.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But, you know, you had, all the time-- you lived, all the time, on a danger level, for all kinds of things.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Something I was afraid what I-- where we sharing room, whether I say something at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Um, all kinds of things were happening at that same time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was cut off from every news around.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Of course, I didn't read in the German news about the-- the-- the Final Solution.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Um, to begin with, when I arrived, you know, Germany was still very victorious.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was later on that-- that-- that things became to-- But to the last minute, they still believed that they have this final weapon, you know, which will solve their solution.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Even-- then everything was disintegrating.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were still hoping that this doodlebug that they've got-- the-- the bomb, the something which will save them in the last minute.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I mean, I'm not giving you a political review.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm just seeing, because a girl was there who was working when her, uh, boyfriend, or-- he was in the Air Force.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So she used to have the news.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "She said, you will see.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "In the last minute, something is coming up that will save us.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
